Edit the file /System/Library/Graphics/Quartz\ Composer\ Plug-Ins/WOTD.plugin/Contents/Resources/NOAD_wotd_list.txt
for your own words.

#########
You may face the SIC issue for Mac OS after 10.11
SIC: System Integrity Protection

To disable it temporarily:
1. boot into recovery mode: restart your Mac and hold Command+R as it boots.
2. Utility -> Terminal
3. csrutil status
4. Now Make it :  csrutil disable
5. after you finished your task : csrutil enable

